datoCmsKey.name: Rachel Heine
datoCmsKey.bio:
AEA Stage Manager based in the Midwest!  Although I am not NYC based, I venture there for shows/contracts from time to time!  I have also spent the last few years on tour and getting a glimpse of what this country has to offer!  

Message me to connect!  I would love to connect with more queer folx in this crazy industry!
